## Attribution Requirements

**If you use this Discord Bot as a base for your own project, please provide proper attribution:**

1. **Include this project as a reference** in your README or documentation
2. **Credit MSCgameplayer** as the original developer
3. **Link back to this repository**: https://github.com/MSCgameplayer/Simple_discord_bot

**Example Attribution:**
```
Based on Simple Discord Bot by MSCgameplayer
Original Project: https://github.com/MSCgameplayer/Simple_discord_bot
```

**Why Attribution Matters:**
This project represents significant development work and effort. Attribution helps support 
the original developer and allows others to find the source project for updates and improvements.

